cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the intersection of wireless communication and machine learning, specifically in the context of edge computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also touches upon system-level issues, which could place it in the cs.SY (Systems and Control) category, and discusses the role of communication in edge learning, which could place it in the cs.IT (Information Theory) category.
